# BlackJack 🃏

A simple terminal-based Blackjack game. Compete against the dealer by trying to get as close to 21 as possible without going over.

## Features
- Full Blackjack rules (hit, stand, bust)
- Dealer logic
- Card deck simulation

## Technologies
- Python (no external libraries)

## What I learned
- Game mechanics and turn-based logic
- Randomization and input handling

## Run the game
```bash
python blackjack.py
